Logical Operators

Operator    Result
&            Logical AND
|            Logical OR
^            Logical XOR (exclusive OR)
||            Short-circuit OR
&&            Short-circuit AND
!            Logical unary NOT
&=            AND assignment
|=            OR assignment
^=            XOR assignment
==            Equal to
!=            Not equal to
?:            Ternary if-then-else


Table
How value of A and B will convert in to logical operators

   A         B            A | B             A & B             A ^ B              !A

  False     False        False             False             False              True

  True      False        True              False             True               False

  False     True         True              False             True               True

  True      True         True              True              False              False



Symbol    Long Name
&    logical AND
&&    conditional AND
|    logical OR
||    conditional OR
!    logical negation (NOT)